	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have tried it on my PAL NES and it ran just fine. Flickering isn't too bad, but I think SHMUPs kinda get it easier in that area because the objects are constantly flying in all directions, whereas in a sidescroller they're often lined up horizontally. Not to mention the chaotic nature of these type of games in general probably lessens the effect even further. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br />In any case, that demo is very well done. I wonder if that's all there is to it, does anybody know what's the current status of the project?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
